{"tid":2053230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局正爭取六月中讓中三至中五跨境學生回港復課","createTime":"2020-06-06T06:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T06:14:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53cc810ecb5d264c60e4e4dd723ce914f1d28201","tid":2053230,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/j6dkLjKBcZ_euP10ZnPm0g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/STUDENT-YEUNG-200606-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fj6dkLjKBcZ_euP10ZnPm0g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FSTUDENT-YEUNG-200606-10.jpg&h=32024c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】教育局局長楊潤雄表示，當局正爭取在六月中，讓中三至中五跨境學生接受核酸檢測後，以特定關口過關，及點對點交通服務等安排下，先行先試回港復課，期望未來一星期落實細節。至於安排會否擴大至其他級別的跨境生，楊潤雄指仍有多項考慮。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄：「在香港這一方，盡量限制他們在香港去甚麼地方，主要是一個關口，然後學校，再回關口，對雙方的信心都大，主要是大家擔心疫情變化。老實說，香港久不久（瀝源邨）又有新個案，對深圳政府難言不擔心，屆時會知道規模可以擴多大，因為再擴大的話，兩個關口夠不夠，還是多開幾個關口，再上已經是大規模上，大家知道小五、小六及中一的跨境學生人數相對上多，與中三至中五相差很遠。」"},{"pid":"2dd2be55089929c12b2606f52ed2d206ae9b0f3e","tid":2053230,"uid":267801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"返嚟做乜，取消放暑假？"},{"pid":"856ae7776a5173edb5f23a43d253a117af69f13b","tid":2053230,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"點解學生可以唔洗隔離14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891110ec3b9fe303f390a478b5e915cdf6063075","tid":2053230,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"快啲啦 第三波社區爆發之後又再停課<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c16a86cf43f7178c1b37a8879fef4f5d803c31","tid":2053230,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,